<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-713] Update Hadoop producer for Kafka 0.8 changes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-713</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With the changes in Kafka 0.8, the Hadoop producer (in contrib) is busted due to changes in the way KeyedMessages are now handled. I will fix.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
